trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> is of type DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref> class.
Adds a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> to add to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.

Adds a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> with the specified URL and value to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
The URL for the reference to add to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> to add to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.

Determines if the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref> contains a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> with the specified URL.
The URL for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> to locate within the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref> contains a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> with the specified URL; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

Gets or sets a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref> with the specified URL.
The URL for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> to get or set from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
An <xref uid="langword_csharp_DiscoveryReference" name="DiscoveryReference" href=""></xref> representing a reference to a discovery document.
Gets an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> object with all the keys in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> containing the keys of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
Removes a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> with the specified URL from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
A string that represents the URL for the object to remove from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
Gets an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> object with all the values in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> containing the values in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection"></xref>.
